messages.text: Where have you been? Haven’t been in school for almost 2 days!!
Just checking. Wanted to make sure you didn’t run away again.
No Just a little...tied up lol
Lol. Guess who I thought I saw today
Outside of Mr.Derrick’s chemistry class. You know he likes to keep the back door open.
I could’ve sworn I saw her. Is she still in that psych ward?
I’m Home. Chris you didn’t answer my question.
Is Alicia still at the psych ward??
Man she was the craziest gf u ever had. That chick was straight loco.
Remember when she found us hanging out and thought we were going together.
It seemed like any girl who thought of getting close to you was doomed if Alicia found out.
What can I say? I know how to pick em.
I heard she’s the one who sliced Maria’s face after she caught you guys studying at the library.
I heard she followed Maria home the next day after school and sliced her face.
Maria’s friend Laney. But Maria refuses to tell anyone what happened.
Is it true that she cut your name into her arms and had a shrine of you in her room?
So that’s the real reason they sent her to the psych ward?
I knew it wasn’t an eating disorder.
Crazy lolol. She had the nerve to blame me for you guys breaking up.
Well she may have been onto something.
I keep a picture of you in my locker and all your school playbills. I even have the tie you gave me for picture day.
No! Not at all. I think I’ve kinda like you too.
I really didn’t think you thought of me that way.
I always thought you were cute and funny. You’re my best friend. It’s funny.
I had a dream a while back that we went on a date and it was amazing at first but turned into a nightmare.
It was on the lake. Then it got weird because I went to get something to drink and when I turned around you were face down tied up in the water.
I tried to swim after you and it was like something started holding me down under then I drowned and jumped out my sleep.
Still talking on it ‘til it dies.
Hold on. Someone rang the doorbell. brb.
Ha. Ha. Ha. No it’s probably MY mom back from the store.
She probably has her hands full and needs me to open the door.
HOW DID YOU KNOW? OMG CHRIS SHE HAS THIS CRAZY LOOK IN HER EYES.
Well didn’t you say she was crazy? Duh! Lol
THIS ISNT A FUCKING LOL MOMENT! IM SERIOUS SHE’S HERE!!!
I’m on the floor behind the front door.
Are you crazy Chris? I thought she was still in the psych ward.
Chris I need you to come and make her go away?
I’m looking through the glass and I think she has a knife.
Bella I’m tied up right now I can’t come.
ARE YOU FUCKING KIDDING ME? YOUR CRAZY EX GF IS HERE AND YOU CANT COME AND HELP ME??
NO! It’ll make a big fuss for nothing. I’m on my way. Are you still by the door?
Listen you should stay in the kitchen.
It’ll be easier to get you
I mean to get you to the neighbors without being seen.
You may need to run next door until I get there.
That’s stupid. She may still be outside.
Behind the island in front of the stove.
Does your bedroom window have a lock on it?
Yes. It has bars on the outside but the lock on the door is broken.
So you won’t be able to get out but at least she won’t be able to get in from outside.
Okay go to your room and stay down.
I told you she was crazy.
I hear something but I don’t know if it’s her.
Please tell me you’re here Chris.
You shouldn’t have left your back door open.
OMG GREAT YOU’RE HERE. COME TO MY ROOM IM IN THE CLOSET.
SCARED TO MOVE.THE DOOR IS UNLOCKED.
THANK YOU CHRIS YOU ARE SAVING MY LIFE!!!
WHY DO I HEAR HEELS? LOL
The one with the small dry board on it. Duh! Did you forget? Lol
Don’t get smart! Chris would know that but I wouldn’t.
